<fig id="Fig2"><label>Fig. 2</label><caption><p>(Color figure online) Representative transverse sections through nodal roots of rice (Oryza sativa cv. DJ123) at both low (<inline-formula id="IEq4"><alternatives><tex-math id="M7">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
