</p></sec><sec id="Sec11"><title>Hair Initiation and Heading</title><p id="Par26">The model requires a start point for each hair and an initial heading. If existing partial hair paths are available (i.e. from SRXCT), a set of all partially visible hair segments (<inline-formula id="IEq23"><alternatives><tex-math id="M45">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
