				\begin{document}$$l_{\mathrm{r},i} $$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M104"><mml:msub><mml:mi>l</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="normal">r</mml:mi><mml:mo>,</mml:mo><mml:mi>i</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="11538_2017_350_Article_IEq52.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. For the rest of its length <inline-formula id="IEq53"><alternatives><tex-math id="M105">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
